@node Main "Linko - Documentation"

                               'Linko' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  The idea of this @{" Workbench game " link play} is to move a 4-branch coloured
'star' from its upper position to the exit, located at the lowest
part of each game board.

  However, small coloured squares as well as 'links' between tiles
have to be moved, and as there is only one empty tile where either
the star or a coloured square can move to, things get a bit more
complicated...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

